    <item>
      <title>IndiGo 的 Gangwal 以接近历史最高价出售 13 亿美元股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/indigo-s-gangwal-sells-1-3-billion-stake-near-record-high</link>
      <description><![CDATA[靛蓝航空的亿万富翁联合创始人拉凯什·甘瓦尔 (Rakesh Gangwal) 出售了该航空公司运营商 InterGlobe Aviation Ltd. 价值近 13 亿美元的股票，而就在前一天，这些股票收于历史高位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/indigo-s-gangwal-sells-1-3-billion-stake-near-record-high</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 09:28:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元普遍疲软，人民币抹平 2024 年跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/china-s-yuan-erases-2024-s-losses-amid-broad-dollar-weakness</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于预期资本将回流中国，且美联储预计将于下个月启动政策宽松周期，中国在岸人民币今年上涨，抹去了损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/china-s-yuan-erases-2024-s-losses-amid-broad-dollar-weakness</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 09:27:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>财政部私募后，中国人民银行从市场购买专项债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/pboc-buys-special-bonds-from-market-after-mof-s-private-auction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国央行周四从市场上购买了特别国债，此举意在将政府通过私募方式展期债务后流动性突然收紧的可能性降至最低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/pboc-buys-special-bonds-from-market-after-mof-s-private-auction</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 09:26:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>凉鞋需求强劲，Birkenstock 确认前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/birkenstock-affirms-outlook-amid-strong-demand-for-sandals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Birkenstock Holding Plc 确认了其 2024 年的财务目标，并报告了强劲的盈利增长，因为消费者抢购了更多高端凉鞋和木屐。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/birkenstock-affirms-outlook-amid-strong-demand-for-sandals</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 09:10:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>董事会考虑发行红股，信实股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/ambani-s-reliance-to-consider-one-on-one-bonus-share-issue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[信实工业有限公司 (Reliance Industries Ltd.) 表示，将考虑发行红股 — — 这是该公司七年来的首次 — — 该公司亿万富翁董事长穆克什·安巴尼 (Mukesh Ambani) 希望在继续向面向消费者的业务多元化发展的过程中吸引小股东。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/ambani-s-reliance-to-consider-one-on-one-bonus-share-issue</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 08:26:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲股市因降息预期上涨，DAX 指数创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/european-stocks-climb-as-rate-outlook-outweighs-tech-jitters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于西班牙通胀数据降温增强了人们对降息的预期，且保乐力加公司 (Pernod Ricard SA) 和 Delivery Hero SE 发布了稳健的盈利预测，欧洲股市上涨至七周高点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/european-stocks-climb-as-rate-outlook-outweighs-tech-jitters</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 07:21:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国表示暂时不会征收关税，人头马和保乐力加股价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/pernod-says-us-china-sales-will-remain-soft-this-quarter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国表示至少目前不会对欧盟白兰地征收临时关税，此后人头马君度集团 (Remy Cointreau SA) 和保乐力加集团 (Pernod Ricard SA) 的股价飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/pernod-says-us-china-sales-will-remain-soft-this-quarter</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 05:27:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
